# CODEOWNERS — review routing for ContextKit
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Catch-all: any path without a more specific match.
*                          @contextkit/maintainers

# Per-package owners
/packages/cli/             @contextkit/maintainers @contextkit/cli-team
/packages/extension/       @contextkit/maintainers @contextkit/extension-team
/packages/web/             @contextkit/maintainers @contextkit/web-team

# Cross-cutting infra
/.github/                  @contextkit/maintainers
/.changeset/               @contextkit/maintainers
/docs/                     @contextkit/maintainers @contextkit/docs-team
/landing/                  @contextkit/maintainers @contextkit/web-team
/templates/                @contextkit/maintainers
